.TH QUASAR-GREP 1 "August 2025" "Quasar Apex" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
quasar-grep \- high-performance text search
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B quasar-grep
[\-h|\-\-help] [\-\-count] [\-\-json] [\fIPATTERN\fR] [\fIFILE\fR...]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B quasar-grep
searches for PATTERN in each FILE. Outputs matches to stdout.
.PP
Options:
.TP
.B \-\-count
Only print the count of matches.
.TP
.B \-\-json
Emit machine-readable JSON summary.
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH EXIT STATUS
Returns 0 on success, non-zero on error.
.SH AUTHORS
Quasar Apex Authors.
